1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,920
Una mesa entera

2
00:00:00,920 --> 00:00:01,480
ahi,

3
00:00:01,480 --> 00:00:02,760
junto al contenedor.

4
00:00:02,760 --> 00:00:03,560
En el Cabañal.

5
00:00:03,560 --> 00:00:04,720
Cuatro muebles.

6
00:00:04,720 --> 00:00:05,560
Una mesa,

7
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:06,400
un somier,

8
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:07,080
un perchero

9
00:00:07,080 --> 00:00:07,760
y una mesita

10
00:00:07,760 --> 00:00:08,560
de noche.

11
00:00:08,560 --> 00:00:08,840
Todo en

12
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:09,440
buen estado.

13
00:00:09,440 --> 00:00:10,600
Todo esperando

14
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:11,080
a que pase

15
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:11,680
el camion.

16
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:12,480
Y esto es

17
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:13,080
lo que mola

18
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:13,560
del Cabañal.

19
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:14,880
Caminas dos calles

20
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:15,600
y te encuentras

21
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:15,880
de todo.

22
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:17,000
Cosas que alguien

23
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:17,600
dejo hace

24
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:18,520
unas horas...

25
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:19,560
que todavia sirven.

26
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:21,040
Que todavia valen.

27
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:21,840
Pero aqui va

28
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:22,560
el dato.

29
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:23,480
Cada semana,

30
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:24,520
muebles como estos

31
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:25,160
acaban en

32
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:26,120
un vertedero.

33
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:26,960
Muebles que podrian

34
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:27,320
estar en

35
00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:28,240
otro salon,

36
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:29,480
en otra habitacion.

37
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:30,200
Con anos de vida

38
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:30,680
por delante.

39
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:31,160
Pues eso

40
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:31,880
tiene solucion.

41
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:32,920
Y es muy facil.

42
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:33,480
En Givore,

43
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:34,120
lo compartes

44
00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:34,560
antes de que

45
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,040
acabe asi.

46
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:35,360
Foto,

47
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:35,720
titulo,

48
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:36,640
publicar.

49
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:37,320
Ya esta visible

50
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:37,680
para quien

51
00:00:37,680 --> 00:00:38,400
lo busque.

52
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:39,080
Y llega entero,

53
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:39,640
sin pasar

54
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:40,560
por la calle.

55
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,040
El perchero

56
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:41,400
y la mesita

57
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:42,320
los subi.

58
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:42,800
Ahora mismo

59
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:43,400
alguien del barrio

60
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:44,080
puede verlos.

61
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:44,800
Asi de rapido.

62
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:45,640
Guardad esto

63
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,520
para cuando veais

64
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:47,520
algo en la calle.

65
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:47,960
O enviadlo

66
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:48,320
a alguien

67
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:48,760
que viva

68
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:49,360
en Valencia.

69
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,360
Givore.

